San_Marcos.Jesmond Dene, California:
Jesmond Dene, an unincorporated community neighboring Escondido in San Diego County, California, lies just east of Interstate 15 north of Escondido and has a zip code of 92026 (as assigned to Escondido). The community is inside area code 760.
It is located at 33°10′49″N 117°6′30″W (33.18028, -117.10833) at an elevation of 900 ft.
